OL,5, The Trades Union Congress (TUC) has    
OL,6, accused the government of refusing to  
OL,7, negotiate on public sector pay.        
OL,9,FIts new general secretary, Paul Nowak, 
OL,10,Fsuggested in a BBC interview that      
OL,11,Fministers were using pay review bodies 
OL,12,F"as a human shield" in negotiations.   
OL,14,FThere has been widespread strike action
OL,15,Fin recent months as prices have soared.
OL,17,FBut the government has said if public  
OL,18,Fsector wages rose in line with the cost
OL,19,Fof living, it would lead to "worsening 
OL,20,Fdebt", leaving "everyone poorer".      
